main event: A report was filed regarding the sighting of three unidentified flying objects over a forested landscape in Sheffield, England on March 4, 1962.
interesting points: The reported UFOs were described as dark, disc-shaped objects,The sighting was documented in Project Blue Book Special Report No. 14,The case number associated with the report is 7824,The photograph included shows the UFOs against a blank sky,The event took place in early March, adding to the historical worth of the documentation.
